  "text": "Few studies are available in the literature on PCT utility in differentiating among Gram-negative, Gram-positive, or fungal bacteremias [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . The aim of the present study was to evaluate PCT ability to discriminate different bacterial or fungal etiology in a large population of patients with documented bloodstream infection.",
